name: NO SLEEP 'TILL 5555
description:
((STRESS LEVEL UNMEASURABLE))

A tribute to the GOGO project (@gogos_tez), created by the amazing @gogoporen and @0x00000010. 

A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono. 

My third experiment at generative art. Prompted an AI to generate a painting based on my original night city photo, and then I animated the result through multi-layered motion techniques to add depth and parallax effects.  

This time, I went further by adding some graphics and drawings.

Jakarta, October 29, 2021.
 1440 × 2160 seamlessly looping MP4.
